duties_responsibilities.duty: Preparation of goods and materials for shipping, inventory maintenance, and compliance with internal control procedures.
Processing material stock requests, orders, and returns using inventory and billing systems.
Handling defective, discontinued, or recalled goods, and performing check-ins and check-outs.
Reviewing the processing of goods received as returns and the return of goods to vendors, and receiving, issuing, and storing supplies and equipment.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma/GED, Off Road Forklift Certification, OSHA Knowledge
